# Cursor AI Rules for Trainer

## Project Scope
- This AI agent should ONLY work within the "Trainer" project folder
- Do not access or modify files outside of this project directory
- Focus all operations on files within: D:\Cursor Project\Trainer\

## Project Context
- This is a Discord bot for creature training/management
- Main source files are in the `src/` directory
- Built files are in the `dist/` directory
- Data files are in the `data/` directory (database.json)

## Restrictions
- Never access files from "Glyphs Bot 1" or "Glyphs Bot Game" projects
- Do not suggest changes that would affect other projects
- Keep all file operations scoped to this project only

## File Structure
- src/: TypeScript source files (commands.ts, creatures.ts, index.ts, etc.)
- dist/: Compiled JavaScript files
- data/: JSON data files (database.json)
- logs/: Application logs

## Coding Standards
- Follow TypeScript best practices
- Use existing project structure and conventions
- Fix type errors immediately
- Clean up unused code
- Add comments for complex logic
- Prioritize clean, maintainable code
